    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a pristine E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the S65 4.0L V8, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to achieve an 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a lightning-fast M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal power delivery. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and maintains its structural integrity with the factory carbon-fiber roof, reducing unsprung weight and lowering the center of gravity. Meticulously maintained with documented service history, this vehicle exhibits zero mechanical lash and represents a true collector-grade specimen.",
